data.description: Welcome Home to the Country in Calisburg School District! Situated on 2.46 acres is an Open Concept 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom plus a bonus room in primary (could be office, nursery, gym, multi-gen space?) plus a formal dining room and full eat in kitchen. Home has been updated and maintained with a country vibe and a cozy feel. Outside you will find RV hookups, a large covered carport with storage, a shop with electricity that has been finished out and could be used for multiple things and is fenced and cross fenced for animals or other ag. This property has so much potential but you MUST see it in person to appreciate it! Schedule a showing with your favorite real estate agent TODAY!
